    "9677792": {
      "title": "On the regularity and uniformness conditions on quadrilateral grids",
      "abstract": "In the literature there are various regularity conditions as well as many different so-called almost parallelogram conditions on the subdivisions of quadrilateral grids. In this paper we investigate and clarify their relations."
